data.name: memoEdit2.EditValue
data.value:
[Country] List of domestic/country/diplomatic information, such as treasury, gdp/etc
[Resources] Contain resource stock, there will be Market Price, Market Production Cost Output efficiency
[Warfare] Warfare are consist of 2 types of Editing object,
1. Unit (Selected Unit) Modifying this value will only change unit stat of the unit u select, upon removal of selection, the unit will not be tracker
2. Unit (Stat of selected Unit [Warfare Editor]), Modifying this value will change the unit original stat.
[Warfare: Calculated option] -Heal - will heal the current selected unit to actual state form. -Rambo - Unit morale/eff/exp overload. -GasSupply2x - Unit current fuel/supply multiplied by 2 -GasSupply4x - Unit current fuel/supply multiplied by 4 -Str2x - Unit current strength Multiplied by 2 -Str4x - Unit current strength Multiplied by 4
[Warfare: Persistent] A List to track godmode unit
[Warfare: Modified] A List to revert/change global modified unit back to original value
[Special] Click Day option - 1 Day Research, Go to research Tab > Select/Hover on queue to complete the selected research - 1 Day Army, Go to defense production > Building X / X - 1 Day Build, Go to land tab, select the building you want to complete (this will not affect AI)
[Special: Facilities] This are not yet implemented, it will contain specific building variables to change (AI Affected), supply level etc.
